00:00:42.540 --> 00:00:45.450
it's relatively straight when you look
down the edge now to keep things

00:00:45.450 --> 00:00:49.050
relatively simple our first sand box is
going to be on the smaller side we can

00:00:49.050 --> 00:00:51.629
